comment: Green (GSW) is in a legal guarding position and is vertical when contact occurs with DeRozan (TOR).
Nogueira (TOR) turns into Green's (GSW) body and affects his movement to the basket.
Curry (GSW) makes contact with DeRozan's (TOR) arm and affects his movement to the basket.
Joseph (TOR) holds Curry (GSW) around the hip, affecting his freedom of movement.
Thompson (GSW) makes contact with Lowry's (TOR) arm while he is in the act of shooting.
Contact by Lowry (TOR) and Green (GSW) is incidental to the rebound attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of a jump ball was overturned.
DeRozan (TOR) slides into Curry (GSW) and commits a blocking foul.
Patterson (TOR) commits a take foul on Thompson (GSW).
Green (GSW) makes contact with Scola's (TOR) arm.
Joseph (TOR) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
